****************************************************************************************************
2D MESH READER
****************************************************************************************************

The purpose of the code is to read a mesh in the MIXD format and write it out as VTK format for
visualization.

## Compilation

To compile the code you have to:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

## Runnning

To run the code you have to:

cd test
../build/read-mesh (./settings.blah.in)

## Visualization

To visualize the result you have to:

module load GRAPHICS paraview
paraview

open Cylinder.pvtu